2026-05-15T22:28:45.2438018Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T22:28:45.2438779Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T22:28:45.2439653Z 230            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-15T22:28:45.2440572Z 231            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-15T22:28:45.2441402Z 232            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
2026-05-15T22:28:45.2442103Z 233            preserve via tools:node="merge".
